replies.bodyText:
It was deliberately added before the JobManager.shutdown, because that method calls into these:
                this.dispatcher.shutdown();
                this.receiver.shutdown();

and the receiver.shutdown() is actually closing the sessions that these threads use.
We don't want to close sessions of threads that are still running, but first wait for the threads to finish

